presentationColumns.name: Dist GL Parent Product Line
presentationColumns.description:
Based On distribution ccid (Segment 5) :

CASE  "SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Dist GL Product Line Segment" 
   WHEN '400' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '410' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '430' then   'MB - SP'
   WHEN '470' then   'MB - Consumables'  
ELSE

  CASE  LEFT("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Dist GL Product Line Segment" , 1)   
    WHEN  '1' THEN 'Systems'
    WHEN  '2' THEN 'FDM-Systems'
    WHEN  '5' THEN 'Consumables'
    WHEN  '6' THEN 'Consumables'
    WHEN  '7' THEN 'FDM-Consumables'
    WHEN  '8' THEN 'Customer Support'
    WHEN  '9' THEN 'FDM-Maintenance and SP'
     ELSE   'Other'
  END
END

presentationColumns.name: Sla GL Parent Product Line
presentationColumns.description:
Based On SLA ((Sub Ledger Account)) ccid (Segment 5) :

CASE  "SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Sla GL Product Line Segment"  
   WHEN '400' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '410' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '430' then   'MB - SP'
   WHEN '470' then   'MB - Consumables'  
   WHEN '393' then   'FDM-Maintenance and SP'  
   WHEN '392' then   'FDM-Maintenance and SP'  
   WHEN '398' then   'Customer Support'  
   WHEN '394' then   'Customer Support'
ELSE

  CASE  LEFT("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Sla GL Product Line Segment"  , 1)   
    WHEN  '1' THEN 'Systems'
    WHEN  '2' THEN 'FDM-Systems'
    WHEN  '5' THEN 'Consumables'
    WHEN  '6' THEN 'Consumables'
    WHEN  '7' THEN 'FDM-Consumables'
    WHEN  '8' THEN 'Customer Support'
    WHEN  '9' THEN 'FDM-Maintenance and SP'
     ELSE   'Other'
  END
END
presentationColumns.sourceLogicalColumn: logicalColumn:SSYS.Dim - Invoice Distribution.Sla GL Parent Product Line

presentationColumns.name: Sla GL Product Line Family
presentationColumns.description:
Based On SLA (Sub Ledger Account) ccid (Segment 5) :

CASE  "SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Sla GL Product Line Segment"  
   WHEN '890' then   'Service'
   WHEN '999' then   'FDM-Service'
   WHEN '400' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '410' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '430' then   'MB - SP'
   WHEN '470' then   'MB - Consumables'  
   WHEN '393' then   'FDM-Maintenance and SP'  
   WHEN '392' then   'FDM-Maintenance and SP'  
   WHEN '398' then   'Customer Support'  
   WHEN '394' then   'Customer Support'

ELSE
   CASE WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Sla GL Product Line Segment" AS DOUBLE)  BETWEEN 101 and 189 THEN 'Equipment'
             WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Sla GL Product Line Segment" AS DOUBLE)    BETWEEN 191 AND 199 THEN 'Equipment Other'  
             WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Sla GL Product Line Segment" AS DOUBLE)  BETWEEN 201 and 271 THEN 'FDM-Equipment'  
             WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Sla GL Product Line Segment" AS DOUBLE)  BETWEEN 272 and 299 THEN 'FDM-Equipment Other'  

   ELSE
      CASE  LEFT("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Sla GL Product Line Segment"  , 1)   
         WHEN  '5' THEN 'Resins'
         WHEN  '6' THEN 'Resins'
         WHEN  '7' THEN 'FDM-Consumable'
         WHEN  '8' THEN 'Service'
         WHEN  '9' THEN 'FDM-Service'
         ELSE   'Other'
      END
   END
END
presentationColumns.sourceLogicalColumn: logicalColumn:SSYS.Dim - Invoice Distribution.Sla GL Product Line Family
